# TecnoFit Project Rules

## Tech Stack
- Frontend: React + Vite + Tailwind CSS
- Backend: Supabase (PostgreSQL + Auth)
- Animations: GSAP (NOT framer-motion)
- Admin Panel: React + Supabase
- Deployment: Vercel

## Always Check
- Tailwind docs: https://tailwindcss.com/docs/installation/using-vite
- Use GSAP for animations, never framer-motion
- Check Figma MCP if design links are provided

## Database Schema
- `prospects`: Website form submissions
- `leads`: Converted prospects
- `users`: Active customers/members
- `sellers`: Staff (front_desk, admin, super_admin) with auth_user_id
- `coaches`: Trainers with auth_user_id, specializations, certifications
- `seller_leads`: Assignment tracking

## Authentication
- Supabase Auth for sellers and coaches
- Login checks sellers table first, then coaches table
- Regular users (customers) are NOT authenticated
- Admin credentials: admin@tecnofit.com / Admin123!

## Project Structure
- `/website/tecno-website`: Public website (cd tecno-website)
- `/website/admin`: Admin panel (cd admin)
- `/tf-backend`: Legacy Strapi (deprecated, DO NOT USE)

## Deployment Workflow
**IMPORTANT:** This repo is connected to Vercel for automatic deployment.

### To Deploy Changes:
1. Make your changes in the appropriate directory:
   - Admin panel: `cd /Users/mataldao/Local/tf-marcopolo/website/admin`
   - Website: `cd /Users/mataldao/Local/tf-marcopolo/website/tecno-website`
2. Commit your changes: `git add . && git commit -m "your message"`
3. Push to GitHub: `git push origin main`
4. Vercel will automatically deploy (takes ~2-3 minutes)

### DO NOT:
- ❌ Use `vercel deploy` command
- ❌ Try to deploy manually
- ❌ Create deployment scripts

### DO:
- ✅ Just commit and push to GitHub
- ✅ Vercel handles deployment automatically
- ✅ Monitor deployment at https://vercel.com/dashboard

### Deployment URLs:
- Admin: https://tecno-admin.vercel.app
- Website: https://somostecnofit.com (or Vercel URL)

